The paper deals with a problem of enabling a team of quadrotors to learn how to accurately track a desired trajectory while holding a given formation in a distributed manner. This involves the use of iterative learning control (ILC) and multi-agent systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
